          <title>Trump threatens attacks on Iranian power plants over opening Strait of Hormuz</title>
          <description><![CDATA[President Donald Trump has warned that the U.S. will “obliterate” Iran’s power plants if it doesn’t fully open the Strait of Hormuz within 48 hours, prompting Tehran to say it would respond to any such strike with attacks on U.S. and Israeli energy and infrastructure assets.]]></description>
